{
  "stem": "21089.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During, actually, after [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the priest has his document and everything was arranged, next Sunday, naturally, like everybody else, was going to the church and I was also going with the people to the church.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the church, I knew exactly what to do because when I was a little boy, I had a nanny.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was-- every Sunday she was going to a Mass, the Catholic church.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was going with her for a walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- I was-- she was taking me to the church.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Naturally, my parents didn't knew about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father wouldn't allow anything like this, for me to go to the church.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, once we went over for a walk on Sunday, and she went to the church and asked if I wanted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't, you know, I was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would say, why not?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would go any place because I didn't know how the church would look when I was-- and when I walk in from the first day was really impressed me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Especially impressed me, those altar boys impressed me in the white robes, and they been marching procession with the big-- with the crosses, with the figures, with and extinguishing the candles, and lighting the candles, and moving and helping the priest.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, this a nice job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I also envied them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I also was thinking gee, I wish I would be an altar boy when I grow up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very small.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, maybe five or so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and since then, every Sunday I want to go to the church.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naturally, my father didn't ask, and I didn't tell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what's normal for a walk, going to be stop in the church.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
